sections.Trivia:
- The names of the suspects come from pool parks[1]:
Nagami Ōiso (大磯 永美) comes from Ōiso Long Beach (大磯ロングビーチ ["Naga" can also mean "long" in Japanese]);
Hamaka Ōiso (大磯 浜香) comes from Ōiso Long Beach (大磯ロングビーチ ["Hama" means "beach" in Japanese]);
Raito Samaki (左巻 頼斗) comes from Tokyo Summerland (東京サマーランド ,Tōkyō Samārando?);
Ensaku Toyoshima (豊島 延策) comes from Toshimaen (としまえん).
